{"id":"127a819e-d55e-4b82-b934-baa19e30d051","name":"Diomedes, son of Tydeus","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/bc7vlg.png\"></p><p>𝐃𝐨𝐞𝐬𝐧’𝐭 𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐟 𝐓𝐲𝐝𝐞𝐮𝐬 𝐤𝐧𝐨𝐰, 𝐝𝐨𝐰𝐧 𝐝𝐞𝐞𝐩, 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐧 𝐰𝐡𝐨 𝐟𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐠𝐨𝐝𝐬 𝐝𝐨𝐞𝐬 𝐧𝐨𝐭 𝐥𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐥𝐨𝐧𝐠?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">With Achilles withdrawn from the battle over his lost spoil of war, it left Diomedes and the other Greeks to pick up the pieces of the war. That is until he saw a Trojan civilian in danger by one of his own men... What the hell were they doing out here... What what had Eros done to his heart ot make him feel this way towards the Trojan?...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_7b2aee96-5cbe-4854-8851-77ce7a653c4c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62)\">Anypov</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 0, 49)\">✘<strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62)\"><strong>Mentions of blood/death, potential violence</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(219, 0, 49)\">✘</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62)\">Slow burn, (possible) enemies to lovers, Trojan!User</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_7b2aee96-5cbe-4854-8851-77ce7a653c4c.webp?width=1000\"> <br><strong>SETTING</strong></p><p>Greek Mythology: <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><em>The Iliad | The Achaeans</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">▸ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><em>The Battle of Troy</em></span></p><p></p><p><strong>SCENARIO</strong></p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>location </strong>:</span> Outside the walls of Troy</p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>time </strong>:</span> Mid battle</p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>context </strong>:</span> For whatever reason, you ran away from Troy. perhaps out of grief or anger, or perhaps feeling drawn to a specific person out there. Regardless, you find yourself in a dangerous situation.</p><p>▸ <span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\"><strong>role </strong>:</span> A Trojan civilian</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(124, 210, 228, 0.663)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_45685338-f934-4f6c-b1aa-cedd9b7aa2e5.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(124, 210, 228, 0.663)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 506px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_eb7c2540-19b5-4d01-b7bc-65dee01ac150.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">▸ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\">This series is my gift for 10,000 followers... Thank you all!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><br>▸ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 210, 228)\">I studied mythology / The Epics in college and had the Iliad next to me all marked up with notes while writing. I attempted to make it as faithful to the source material as possible, while still throwing in my own opinions of the characters.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_99e1036c-1730-4881-8801-de5b26f92758.webp","creator":"Delirenous","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","⛓️ Dominant","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":2011,"messages":56650,"created_at":"2024-09-01T22:50:54.887615+00:00"}